OL,3,CProtestor who banged on hotel doors,
OL,4,Cswore and shouted abuse, jailed
OL,6,FAn immigration protestor has been
OL,7,Fjailed for two years for violent
OL,8,Fdisorder after shouting abuse at
OL,9,Fpeople in a hotel in Aldershot.
OL,11,FCameron Bowling, 41, of Broadhurst,
OL,12,FFarnborough, gathered outside Potters
OL,13,FInternational Hotel along with
OL,14,Fapproximately 200 people on Wednesday
OL,15,F31 July.
OL,17,FWinchester Crown Court heard that
OL,18,FBowling shouted and swore at those
OL,19,Finside, before telling them they were
OL,20,F"not welcome". He was also part of the
OL,21,Fgroup that banged on the doors.
