OL,3,CProtestor who banged on hotel doors,
OL,4,Cswore and shouted abuse, jailed
OL,6,FSome in the wider group were seen
OL,7,Fthrowing objects at the hotel before
OL,8,Fbanging on the doors. Others acted in
OL,9,Fa threatening way towards those
OL,10,Fstaying inside the hotel.
OL,12,FBowling was arrested and charged with
OL,13,Fviolent disorder. He pleaded guilty to
OL,14,Fthe charge and was today (23
OL,15,FSeptember) jailed for two years at
OL,16,FWinchester Crown Court.
OL,18,FIt comes after three men were jailed
OL,19,Ffor being part of the group that was
OL,20,Finvolved in the violent disorder at
OL,21,Fthe same protest.
