OL,3,CProtestor who banged on hotel doors,
OL,4,Cswore and shouted abuse, jailed
OL,6,FClive Patfield, 60, of The Chantrys,
OL,7,FFarnham, was jailed for two years,
OL,8,Fwhile Kieron Marney, 25, of Fairview
OL,9,FRoad, Ash, was jailed for two years
OL,10,Fand three months. They both pleaded
OL,11,Fguilty to violent disorder and were
OL,12,Fjailed on 4 September.
OL,14,FPerrie Fisher, 28, of Hillside Road,
OL,15,FFarnham, pleaded guilty to violent
OL,16,Fdisorder and failing to surrender to
OL,17,Fpolice / court bail at the appointed
OL,18,Ftime. He was jailed for 29 months on
OL,19,F20 August.
