OL,4,Cswore and shouted abuse, jailed
OL,6,FMeanwhile, Alby Brannan, 18, of
OL,7,FWinchester Road, Ash, pleaded guilty
OL,8,Fto violent disorder and is due to be
OL,9,Fsentenced on 29 November.
OL,11,FA 13-year-old girl from Aldershot, who
OL,12,Fcannot be named for legal reasons, was
OL,13,Falso charged with violent disorder and
OL,14,Fadmitted the charge at Basingstoke
OL,15,FMagistrates Court on 13 August. She
OL,16,Fwas bailed and is due to be sentenced
OL,17,Fat the same court on 30 September.
