OL,3,CProtestor who banged on hotel doors,
OL,4,Cswore and shouted abuse, jailed
OL,6,FJamie Lee Turvey, 34, of Montgomery
OL,7,FRoad, Farnborough, denied the offence
OL,8,Fand is due to go on trial on 14 April
OL,9,F2025.
OL,11,FAsst Ch Con Paul Bartolomeo said:
OL,12,F"While the majority of people who
OL,13,Fattended this protest in Aldershot
OL,14,Fwere respectful, Bowling chose to act
OL,15,Fin an aggressive manner.
OL,17,F"His behaviour that day caused fear of
OL,18,Fviolence to those inside the hotel and
OL,19,Four officers.
