OL,4,Cswore and shouted abuse, jailed
OL,6,F"This result highlights that this sort
OL,7,Fof behaviour will not be tolerated and
OL,8,Fit is a clear message that these
OL,9,Factions have consequences.
OL,11,F"This should serve as a warning to
OL,12,Fanyone else considering trying to
OL,13,Fbring mindless violence to our streets
OL,14,Fand that the minority who seek to
OL,15,Fcause disorder will face the full
OL,16,Fforce of the law."
